  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"StartAbsoluteValue x minus 2 EndAbsoluteValue equals 9\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mfenced close=\"|\" open=\"|\">\n\t\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t\t\t<mo>-</mo>\n\t\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t</mfenced>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>9</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">What is one possible solution to the given equation?</p>",
